# Core JOT Rules

- Project code is Go v1.20+
- Use only Go standard library - Do NOT use third party packages
- Document code using comments and explanations in 'README.dev.md'
- Adhere to SOLID, DRY, KISS, YAGNI principles
- Separation of concerns in different files
- Adhere to the Principle of least privilege, if applicable
- Keep files short and easily readable